title: Bug 114470[Smoke] Error message throws when using new Date('3/2/2005') as value in table filter.
description: When trying to use the value 'new Date('3/2/2005')' in a table filter, an error message is displayed.
OB: On attempting to use the value 'new Date('3/2/2005')' in a table filter, an error message is thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the table filter.
2. Enter 'new Date('3/2/2005')' as the filter value.
3. Observe the error message that is displayed.
